display="inline"><![CDATA[h\in  H]]></fr:tex> and <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[k\in  K]]></fr:tex> and
<fr:tex
display="block"><![CDATA[(h,k)(h',k')=(h\cdot \varphi (k)h',kk')]]></fr:tex>
is its binary operator.</fr:p>
 
   
